title: DDFP 243: Reid on Kaepernick vs. Wilson & NFL vs. College
itunes:title: DDFP 243: Reid on Kaepernick vs. Wilson & NFL vs. College
description:
Shek, Rank and Handsome Hank chat with San Francisco 49ers Pro Bowl safety Eric Reid about Richard Sherman and the Seattle Seahawks, Colin Kaepernick vs. Russell Wilson, a college team's chances vs. an NFL team and much more. The guys also pick winners of the second-round matchups in "NFL.com's Bracketology: The Greatest QB of All Time" tournament.
